# AI Assistant (Phase 57) — the bundled local LLM model file (~941MB) is a
# downloadable build asset, not source. Committing it would bloat the repo
# from ~33MB to ~1GB permanently (git history never shrinks without a
# rewrite). Place Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct-Q4_K_M.gguf here manually before
# running a real installer build (npm run dist) — see resources/models/README.md.
resources/models/*.gguf
